---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Next.js & Astro Web Applications" 
  description="High-performance custom web applications built using Next.js, Astro, React, and Tailwind CSS. Edge-optimized delivery with sub-second page loads."
>
  <section class="relative pt-36 pb-20 overflow-hidden bg-surface">
    <!-- Backlights -->
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-primary-maroon/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,rgba(193,199,207,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,rgba(193,199,207,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:4rem_4rem] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 relative z-10">
      
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-primary-accent hover:text-white transition-colors uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-8 focus:outline-none">
        ← Back to Overview
      </a>

      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div class="max-w-[800px] mb-16">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-purple-500/20 bg-purple-500/5 text-[10px] font-bold text-purple-400 tracking-[0.1em] uppercase mb-4">
          The Performance Frontier
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-6">
          Custom JS Frameworks. <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-silver via-white to-primary-accent bg-clip-text text-transparent">Sub-Second Delivery.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-secondary-silver leading-relaxed">
          For SaaS platforms, tech startups, and complex web applications requiring custom databases and state models. We write custom React/Astro solutions deployed directly onto global edge CDN networks.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Specs & Performance Highlights -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-20">
        <div class="p-6 border border-outline-ghost bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/70 font-semibold block mb-2">Response Speed</span>
          <span class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white block mb-1">&lt;0.3s TTFB</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-secondary-silver">Sub-second time-to-first-byte measurements via distributed edge servers.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border border-outline-ghost bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/70 font-semibold block mb-2">Build Optimization</span>
          <span class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white block mb-1">Zero JS Overhead</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-secondary-silver">Astro server-side layouts shipping flat HTML without script bloat.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border border-outline-ghost bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/70 font-semibold block mb-2">Interactive Depth</span>
          <span class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white block mb-1">State Machines</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-secondary-silver">Advanced dashboard states, reactive data lists, and client pipelines.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-20" id="edge">
        
        <!-- Left Column: Key Features -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">Custom React & Astro Capabilities</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-default bg-primary-maroon/20 border border-primary-accent/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-accent shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">01</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-2">Next.js Web Applications</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant/90 leading-relaxed">
                  Building dashboards and SaaS tools using Next.js App Router. We configure Server Actions, route handlers, and custom database pipelines (Supabase, PostgreSQL, Prisma) to process millions of nodes safely.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-default bg-primary-maroon/20 border border-primary-accent/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-accent shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">02</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-2">Astro Static Content Engines</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant/90 leading-relaxed">
                  Creating lightning-fast static assets. By leveraging Astro's content collections, markdown compilers, and server-side components, we output high-performance landing hubs with zero redundant Javascript.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-default bg-primary-maroon/20 border border-primary-accent/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-accent shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">03</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-white mb-2">Custom Database & API Systems</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant/90 leading-relaxed">
                  Integrating custom inventory schemas, CRM databases, or secure payment gateways (Stripe Connect). We write clean backend routes to protect data flows and maintain speed targets.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column: Specs Card -->
        <div class="p-8 border border-outline-ghost/40 bg-surface-container rounded-lg relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-primary-maroon/10 rounded-full blur-2xl pointer-events-none"></div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs border-b border-outline-ghost/20 pb-4">Custom Framework Specifications</h3>
          
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-outline-ghost/20">
                <td class="py-3 font-semibold text-secondary-silver">Framework Layer</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-right text-white">Next.js, Astro Core, React.js</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-outline-ghost/20">
                <td class="py-3 font-semibold text-secondary-silver">CSS Processing</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-right text-white">Tailwind CSS v4 CSS-first setup</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-outline-ghost/20">
                <td class="py-3 font-semibold text-secondary-silver">State Managers</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-right text-white">Zustand, React Context, TanStack Query</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-outline-ghost/20">
                <td class="py-3 font-semibold text-secondary-silver">Database & ORM</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-right text-white">Prisma, Drizzle ORM, Supabase</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 font-semibold text-secondary-silver">CDN Hosting</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-right text-white">Vercel, Netlify, Custom Cloud VPS</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          
          <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-ghost/50 rounded-default text-xs text-on-surface-variant">
            <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Tailwind CSS v4 Configuration:</strong> Our styling compiles to tiny raw CSS sheets. We use v4's modern CSS variables blocks for instant styling and layouts rendering.
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Action Footer -->
      <div class="p-8 border border-primary-accent/20 bg-primary-maroon/5 rounded-lg flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">Ready to engineer a custom web application?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-secondary-silver">Book a tech strategy call to map your SaaS database schema or platform roadmap.</p>
        </div>
        <a 
          href="/#contact" 
          class="w-full sm:w-auto px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white bg-primary-maroon border border-primary-accent/40 rounded-default glow-btn-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-lg text-center"
        >
          Book Strategy Call
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
